他新闻主题时提供了不准确的答案。他写道，聊天机器人在回答有关外交政策的问题时也依赖官方媒体。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;彭博社的新报道&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/eSimc0BAuc_WeGOQfuSylnUWRSnLxZYdRDYgzlG6d22B64CsFTw2SlqKC3UIwSIiSVYvPwkIKTtudG-MVrReiwBAU0-3FMysMRRol0sudIv9xlhDqug255sCd6Igm8-NvMpojewo3tPJn2njF8SzK65uUqkvc_AzYk3vV93LIq3BzuceSZeg5P5PhjIBCkyTNg6RTJrHMUjILBTMai-PpeKO48l0CdviITuLe-OoE63md3I-PGjnf2dIL1U2KlCa9hqGmAFjeCuujSuLniSKIuUYqJ4Y1qna09SNlA2MoPv2ztt4TsDwRiaKexCQ-Sx8tZYR/RWAO_ND1V_imiEd0M1qSRCdH1LCxbLfO/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="今日人工智能"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;获取《今日人工智能》时事通讯&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;——通过彭博全球新闻编辑室的分析，记录人工智能对企业、工人、政府和经济造成的破坏和威胁。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;走之前... &lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 24px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/gCGF5E99_fYTdkEUa432qbzD1PhFooJJKMjIqKIVJYlgJwev2EVnPoqWF-SrH3Mo386mo4jDFSR_c-hlGrIc2F8XM71SWsBEX1NmaDxq-rBMBHHhjfg9RTz4Z3iA1e_Lx-0UgxXFqxwkAtEFQkD0FlezTYCM88l-33SIXa4QlpPjqFVsEGJ3L3Ue7ERNXGUU1p1fAkiOH1O_M8_x2E0kxNvInUWxIy79JHOpBy_Yh0Ezz8CAhtBIsw_jrLEFee_EvJxgP9AapeYjUys5JDKF26Eakxs8ERijdnz-HJoRqnTXAJpddSnkLytb_5whBdyFkYelVekVLg72rUjyJBZU43VT7W8zPIRCl15JP9-BuCkdsuL1Uiyybjmt14SvNsOUXOWIWblfe7C6_A72OA/1SOX9RBvi_mHzEivhMBE6lBdwjyC3jZ2/20" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i72h6G5FHOUE/v1/-1x-1.jpg" alt="Fans arrive at Allegiant Stadium before a Las Vegas Raiders game in Las Vegas." width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&